## Board Troubleshooting

- **Timeout/connection reset**: Try different ports (1116, 1117). The board may be in use.
- **"Error on opening .bin"**: Ensure `-DGETENV_TESTDIR` is set (run_fpga_test.sh handles this automatically).
- **"Environment call from M-mode"**: Binary may be missing `-mvh` flag (run_fpga_test.sh handles this automatically).
- **First_Reset_done**: The script deletes this file before each run to ensure clean board initialization.
